        • cacheObjNamesRefs

          java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​AnimatedGuiObjectCV> cacheObjNamesRefs
          A cache to map the names of the objects in the group to the corresponding object references. Note that the mapping is not necessarily up to date - e.g. because objects have left or joined the group or have changed their names. Therefore, this mapping should be used only through the findObjectByName() method.
